ent-RMCJumpsuitSPPSOF-name = CCC5-L compression undersuit
ent-RMCJumpsuitSPPSOF-desc = A temperature-regulating pressure suit forming the base layer of the CCC5-L system. It provides compression support, limited vacuum resistance, moisture-wicking properties, and NBC protection to sustain operators in hazardous conditions.

ent-RMCJumpsuitSPPMariner-name = SPP Mariner Fatigues
ent-RMCJumpsuitSPPMariner-desc = A set of SPP fatigues specifcially designed for Marines and Mariners.

ent-RMCJumpsuitSPPOfficerShirt-name = SPP Officer's Shirt
ent-RMCJumpsuitSPPOfficerShirt-desc = A well-tailored off-white shirt and pants, designed for officers who don't use fatigues.

